dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.eventing
Class TreeTableSelectionEvent

java.lang.Object
  dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.eventing.WidgetSelectionEvent
      dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.eventing.TreeTableSelectionEvent

public class TreeTableSelectionEvent
extends WidgetSelectionEvent

The event is fired as a WidgetSelectionEvent by SWTTreeTable instances.

This event provides:

  • Row and column of the clicked cell of the last mouse click
  • Currently selected rows
